scene.message:
Nanjo: The archive room is{nl}
further in. Shall we go{nl}
take a look?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Hmm, a receptionist,{nl}
huh... Hmm...{wait_fr:48} It's got a{nl}
nice ring to it, though.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: A field trip before{nl}
we even go for the hospital{nl}
exam?{wait_fr:32} ...What a weirdo!{waitkey}{ret}

Receptionist: Welcome to the{nl}
Mikage Local History Museum!{waitkey}{clearbox}Here we house materials vital{nl}
to understanding the region's{nl}
history.{waitkey}{ret}
